high_descs: Turn right and three steps, turn left and walk to the right sink and stop.
Pick up the green scrub sponge.
Bend down, holding the sponge.
Place the sponge on the counter top, horizontally, just to the right of the spray bottle.
Turn left and take four steps, turn right and face the sink.
Pick up the green scrub sponge.
Turn right and take four steps, turn left to face the other sink.
Place the sponge on the counter top, horizontally, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place two scrub sponges on the opposite sides of a sink.

high_descs: Take a step to the right to face the right side of the sink.
Pick up the sponge in the sink.
Look down to face the edge of the bathroom sink.
Place the sponge on the edge of the counter between the sinks.
Take a step to the left to face the sink of the left side.
Pick up the sponge in the sink.
Take a step back to face the counter between the sinks.
Place the sponge next to the first sponge in the middle between the sinks.
anns.task_desc: To move two sponges from inside the sinks to the counter between the sinks.

high_descs: Walk to the right side of the sink.
Take the sponge out of the sink.
Look towards the edge of the counter.
Put the sponge down on the counter to the left of the sink.
Walk to the front of the sink on the left.
Pick up the sponge from the sink.
Walk back to the front of the sink on the right side.
Put the sponge down on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move two sponges to the counter.
